@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_potukx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.15)) / ((v0 + 0.76 + v2 + 0.81) + (v1 + 0.97 * v1 + 0.97)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.10)) * (0.61 - (tmp + 0.07 - v0 + 0.80)))
    v1 = (0.42 * wp.sin(0.74))
    v2 = ((v2 + v1) - wp.sin((v1 + 0.02 - v1 + 0.86)))
    data[tid] = v0
